parameters: Village Chief Olden: I'm counting on you.

Village Chief Olden: Thanks to all of you, I have been able
to repair my relationship with Phoni over time.

Village Chief Olden: Clea, is there something you need
today?
Clea: I came here today to discuss something.

Village Chief Olden: I see... Strange sounds, an immortal
knight, you say?

Thief Nora: I have this unpleasant feeling of a ringing in
my ears! Just being near it made me feel sick!

Mage Relm: I haven't heard of such magic even at the Magic
Academy. If there was magic like that, the military would
have already put it into practical use.

Village Chief Olden: Phoni, stop hiding and come over
here!

Village Chief Olden: Phoni, do you want to be of help to
everyone?

Voice Priestess Phoni: Of course! Clea-san and the others
are our saviors...

Village Chief Olden: It is likely the work of the cursed
demon Giloran. There is a tale in our clan's tradition about
an immortal sorcerer.

Mage Relm: Isn't it a lost magic...! So that means we don't
know how to break it, right?
Voice Priestess Phoni: That's not true.

Voice Priestess Phoni: The priestess inherits the [Voice]
of the previous generations from the clan. Among them, there
are voices that have broken Giloran's magic.

Village Chief Olden: Go, Phoni. Go and assist your
benefactors in this village above all else.
Voice Priestess Phoni: Yes... Thank you very much!
Clea: Thank you for your cooperation.

Voice Priestess Phoni: Hehe, I'm glad I can be of help to
Clea-san.
Voice Priestess Phoni: Now, let's go together.

Village Chief Olden: Thanks to all of you, I have been able
to repair my relationship with Phoni over time.
3.イベント後のプレイヤーの位置

Village Chief Olden: Thank you for coming today. Please
allow me and my daughter to welcome everyone.

Thief Nora: Everything here is delicious! It's a shame
Armada-san couldn't come too~

Mage Relm: As a researcher, that's how it goes. I hear
you're writing a book, so I'm looking forward to its
completion!

Priestess Sophia: As expected, this wine is delicious. It's
even more exceptional when it doesn't have sleeping pills in
it, isn't it?

Village Chief Olden: I truly apologize for my rudeness at
that time. As the representative of this village and as an
individual, please allow me to apologize.

Priestess Sophia: Hehe, that was just a joke. But more
importantly, is it okay for your daughter to be like that?

Priestess Phoni: Clea-san, how about this!? I picked wild
herbs and cooked this dish myself. This cuisine here is--

Village Chief Olden: I may be laughed at for being a doting
parent, but my daughter, who has been revered as a
priestess, is laughing with friends of the same age.

Village Chief Olden: As a parent, that is something that
brings me great joy.

Priestess Phoni: Clea-san, please try this dish too! I
specially set aside a larger portion for you, so come on!

Clea: I can eat it alone, and besides, isn't it quite
close?

Village Chief Olden: However, I don't want her to lose her
dignity as a priestess.
3.イベント後のプレイヤーの位置

Village Chief Olden: I cannot thank you enough. Even though
we are far apart, I will offer my prayers.

Village Chief Olden: Thank you for coming. I would like you
to defeat the beasts that come to the village right away.

Clea: Understood, we will respond immediately, but won't we
be able to request assistance from the Imperial Guards?

Village Chief Olden: We do not trust the Empire. I have
heard that the Adventurer's Guild is an independent entity
within the Empire.

Village Chief Olden: ...Let's stop here. Please refrain
from prying into our affairs any further.
Clea: Understood. We will go and subjugate them.

Village Chief Olden: Please accept your reward, and I
apologize for my rudeness earlier.

Village Chief Olden: I never expected guests from the Magic
Academy!

Mage Relm: Hehe, it seems like you finally realized my
worth!

Village Chief Olden: It may be modest, but I would like to
offer you all some hospitality...

Mage Relm: Hehe, it's fine. It's like a hospitality just
for me, isn't it?

Village Chief Olden: Well then, please wait a moment as I
prepare.

Thief Nora: This is delicious, and this one is delicious
too!

Priestess Sophia: Ahaha, this wine is also excellent, isn't
it~♪

Village Chief Olden: Please eat to your heart's content and
I hope it will help you relax and heal your fatigue.

Village Chief Olden: By the way, did you come with any
requests from the Magic Academy?

Mage Relm: That kind of talk is a secret, but I'll make an
exception and tell you today--

Clea: Relm-san, who came from the Adventurer's Guild, is
just my collaborator.
Mage Relm: Hey, let me answer that!
Village Chief Olden: I see... I'm relieved to hear that.

Village Chief Olden: No, this is about our village's
specialty. Please enjoy it to your heart's content.

Thief Nora: Huh... I'm starting to feel sleepy for some
reason...

Priestess Sophia: Oh my, I'm starting to feel a bit tipsy
too...

Village Chief Olden: It might be the fatigue from your long
journey. Please rest here and take your time to relax.

Voice Priestess Phoni: Clea, you came to play! If you'd
like, please try the dish I made!

Voice Priestess Phoni: I'm happy that I can now be treated
as a daughter, not just as a priestess, and have been able
to talk to Father more than before.
